@FraudDetectionSystem_HostAddress = https://localhost:7263

### 1. Get demo stores
GET {{FraudDetectionSystem_HostAddress}}/api/Store
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Get demo customers
GET {{FraudDetectionSystem_HostAddress}}/api/Customer
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. SAFE invoice - normal daytime gold purchase
POST {{FraudDetectionSystem_HostAddress}}/api/Monitoring/process-invoice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceNumber": "INV-1001",
  "customerId": 1,
  "storeId": 1,
  "employeeId": 1,
  "transactionType": 1,
  "itemCategory": 1,
  "amount": 85000,
  "paymentMethod": "UPI",
  "invoiceCustomerName": "Rahul Sharma",
  "paymentCustomerName": "Rahul Sharma",
  "hasOfferApplied": false,
  "transactionDate": "2026-06-20T14:30:00Z"
}

###

### 4. FRAUD invoice - payment name mismatch + high cash
POST {{FraudDetectionSystem_HostAddress}}/api/Monitoring/process-invoice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceNumber": "INV-1002",
  "customerId": 2,
  "storeId": 1,
  "employeeId": 1,
  "transactionType": 1,
  "itemCategory": 2,
  "amount": 350000,
  "paymentMethod": "CASH",
  "invoiceCustomerName": "Priya Patel",
  "paymentCustomerName": "Unknown Person",
  "hasOfferApplied": false,
  "transactionDate": "2026-06-20T22:30:00Z"
}

###

### 5. RETURN after offer - suspicious return
POST {{FraudDetectionSystem_HostAddress}}/api/Monitoring/process-invoice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceNumber": "RET-2001",
  "customerId": 1,
  "storeId": 1,
  "employeeId": 2,
  "transactionType": 2,
  "itemCategory": 1,
  "amount": 84000,
  "paymentMethod": "CASH",
  "invoiceCustomerName": "Rahul Sharma",
  "paymentCustomerName": "Rahul Sharma",
  "hasOfferApplied": false,
  "transactionDate": "2026-06-21T11:00:00Z"
}

###

### 6. Get all fraud alerts
GET {{FraudDetectionSystem_HostAddress}}/api/FraudAlert
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Daily monitoring report
GET {{FraudDetectionSystem_HostAddress}}/api/Report/daily/1?date=2026-06-20
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Store summary report
GET {{FraudDetectionSystem_HostAddress}}/api/Report/store-summary
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. All transactions with fraud scores
GET {{FraudDetectionSystem_HostAddress}}/api/Monitoring/transactions
Accept: application/json

###
